'''Controversy''' is a subhead often used on [[Wikipedia]] to attack a person or group without being red-lighted for [[Criteria for Speedy Deletion|G10]].  Often, controversy sections are unintentionally [[lulzy]] as the subject has been flagged for excessive [[drama]].

